---
title: Creamy Sausage Orzo with Baby Spinach and Mushrooms
description: Busy weeknight? Let's get you sorted with this dreamy, creamy herby orzo! This one's a little lighter as the hero is that magical component that brings every pasta dish together: pasta water!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/orzo-cremeux-aux-saucisses-85057f68.jpg
